00:52:50.640 --> 00:52:52.950
So here, we're going
to attempt something

00:52:52.950 --> 00:52:55.040
a little more general.

00:52:55.040 --> 00:53:04.620
I'll put an exponential minus
1/2, and what should I put?

00:53:04.620 --> 00:53:09.700
Well, let's try to be
